caption: This song contains a piano playing a melody in the mid range and also in the higher register. A flute is adding another melody in the mid range. A digital drum is holding a simple groove before dropping out completely. A male voice is softly rapping/talking in the mid range then another male with an effect takes over singing in a higher pitch. In the background you can hear strings underlaying chords. This song may be playing with headphones daydreaming.
